  "2026-05-23T04:18:33.981Z",claude-code-agent,"PR #45 opened (branch agent-ux-deps-graph-batch-20260523, commit 398fb079). Full local gate green: 1473 tests / 100% coverage; check-secrets clean; manual temp-dir smoke for all 8 findings passed. Awaiting CI + AI-bot review (>=15min) before merge. Follow-up pm-swie filed for the update/create --test parser consistency."
  "2026-05-23T04:26:28.854Z",claude-code-agent,"CI feedback cycle 1: PR #45 'Gates (static)' failed — pm-kyd6 additions pushed runUpdate cyclomatic complexity 257->264 over the 260 budget. Fixed in commit 316284ef by extracting resolveBlockedByDependencyTarget + applyBlockedByDependencyEdge module-level helpers (pure refactor; behavior unchanged). Re-verified locally: full build OK, 1473 tests / 100% coverage, static gate passes. Pushed; awaiting CI re-run + AI-bot review."
  "2026-05-23T04:45:07.903Z",claude-code-agent,"AI-bot review (all CI green: gates+tests+CodeRabbit+Sourcery+Gemini+codex). Actionable feedback to address: (1) gemini HIGH: type-guard document.metadata.blocked_by before .trim() in update.ts (crash risk; close.ts already guards). (2) coderabbit/codex MAJOR: semantic-degraded warning says results_are_lexical, but pure semantic mode returns empty hits (only hybrid includes keyword hits) -> make accurate / graceful. (3) coderabbit MAJOR: --status added to LIST_FILTER_FLAG_CONTRACTS but maybe not to TOOL_LIST_FILTER_OPTION_CONTRACTS -> verify list tool schema sync. (4) sourcery: duration path rejects equal start/end (zero duration) vs instant-event semantics -> align. (5) gemini/coderabbit: close.ts clear blocked_reason even without blocked_by + clear orphan blocked_by edges if scalar missing. (6) gemini HIGH: unresolved --blocked-by sets scalar+no edge (asymmetry) -> warn (never-block, mirrors parent-missing pattern). (7) sourcery/gemini: extract duplicated resolveEventEndAt to shared module. (8) coderabbit minor: CHANGELOG attribution pm-uzmf/CAL1. (9) coderabbit: harden S1 test with count/id. NOTE: coderabbit '.agents/pm direct edit' is a false positive (changes are pm-CLI-generated, not hand edits)."
  "2026-05-23T04:57:28.811Z",claude-code-agent,"Review-feedback round committed (993584e7) addressing all 4 bots: (1) update.ts type-guard blocked_by; (2) unresolved --blocked-by warns (blocked_by_unresolved, non-blocking); (3) search semantic empty-corpus degrades to keyword hits so results_are_lexical is accurate; (4) cli-contracts status added to TOOL_LIST_FILTER_OPTION_CONTRACTS; (5) close clears blocked_reason + orphan edges independently; (6) resolveEventEndAt de-duplicated into event-validation-messages.ts + zero-duration instant. CHANGELOG attribution clarified. 5 new/updated regression tests. Re-verified: 1473 tests/100% coverage, static gate passes, check-secrets clean. PR reply posted. Awaiting CI re-run + bot re-review."
  "2026-05-23T05:21:23.676Z",codex-review-fixer,"Evidence: PR #45 remaining non-outdated Codex reviewer threads addressed: search degraded warning now says no_vector_matches rather than false no_embedded_items; semantic mode still returns lexical fallback when vector ranking contributes no hits; cmd alias now preserves comma-containing command payloads via parse continuation; update --blocked-by prunes all stale blocked_by edges before adding the scalar blocker edge. Verification: pnpm build; focused linked pm test passed 3 files/123 tests; full gate passed 100 files/1478 tests/100% coverage; pnpm quality:static passed; node scripts/check-secrets.mjs passed."
